---
// Update the filename/extension if you switch from PNG to JPG
const photo = '/images/profile_pic.png';
---

<section id="about" class="py-24 px-6">
  <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto">

    <p class="reveal text-accent text-sm font-medium uppercase tracking-widest mb-4">About</p>

    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-16 items-center">

      <!-- Text -->
      <div>
        <h2 class="reveal text-4xl font-bold text-[#f5f5f7] mb-6 leading-tight">
          Building data systems<br />that actually get used.
        </h2>
        <div class="reveal space-y-4 text-[#a1a1a6] text-lg leading-relaxed" style="animation-delay:0.1s">
          <p>
            I'm a Data Infrastructure Engineer based in Michigan. Over 5+ years I've designed pipelines
            that process billions of events per month, built cloud data platforms that serve executive
            decision-making, and created visualizations that turn complex datasets into clear stories.
          </p>
          <p>
            Before my MS in Computer Science at UT Arlington, I built the data backbone for smart
            wearables at KaHa Technologies — real-time health analytics at 10M+ user scale. I care
            deeply about the full stack: from ingestion architecture to the dashboard someone actually
            opens every morning.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="reveal mt-8 flex flex-wrap gap-3" style="animation-delay:0.2s">
          <span class="badge">AWS</span>
          <span class="badge">dbt</span>
          <span class="badge">Apache Spark</span>
          <span class="badge">Kafka</span>
          <span class="badge">Snowflake</span>
          <span class="badge">Python</span>
          <span class="badge">D3.js</span>
          <span class="badge">Airflow</span>
        </div>

        <p class="reveal mt-8 text-[#6e6e73] text-sm" style="animation-delay:0.3s">
          ⚡ Outside of data: racket sports 🏸🎾🏓, music 🎸, cooking 🧑‍🍳 —
          and yes, I once <a href="https://drive.google.com/file/d/1VNMML9SCU_KENcqndlxAjtqMP5y43bFL/view?usp=sharing" target="_blank" class="text-accent hover:underline">worked as a chef</a> for my university's catering department.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Photo -->
      <div class="reveal flex justify-center md:justify-end" style="animation-delay:0.15s">
        <div class="relative">
          <!-- Glow ring -->
          <div class="absolute inset-0 rounded-full bg-accent opacity-10 blur-2xl scale-110"></div>
          <img
            src={photo}
            alt="Ravi Rajpurohit"
            class="relative w-72 h-72 rounded-full object-cover border-2 border-[#2d2d2f]"
            onerror="this.src='/images/profile_pic.jpg'"
          />
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</section>
